This is part of the NPCI Upi Simulator Project.
This is the PSP/Bank Server.
It contains both PSP and Bank. but both having separate controllors.
PSP is the only one in contact with the app.

The flow:
app <-> psp <-> npci <-> bank

It contains the endpoint for the following features:
1. To fetch user info.
2. Initiate a transaction.
3. Check account balance.
4. Fetch NPCI public keys.
5. Register App's CL with NPCI.
